{
  "stem": "8775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All these things get kind of blurry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] After 50 years, these things are kind of blurry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know it was a what they called in German [GERMAN], which was a concentration camp for transit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were thousands and thousands of people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they all arrived from, from various wagons and from various parts of the countries, not only from Hungary but from other parts of other countries as well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, mind you, that Hungary was the last country which actually was taken by Hitler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we are the last ones who got, got being exterminated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nevertheless, when we arrived, we had, again, no idea where we are and what the situation will be here, what the circumstances will bring.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just hope that we can survive from one day to the next.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was, that was also a crucial thing, especially in my physical state and in my physical condition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother-- thank God.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was fairly strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I said before, she knew the, the German language perfectly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She sounded like a real, true German, with her, her [GERMAN] accent, with high German accent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that, that served for our advantage all the, all the years, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But Strasshof we managed-- people from Szolnok managed together, together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And finally, when the call came that they needed people for work in, in Austria, then 21 people said that they, they want to go together.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And these were the people from Szolnok.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Strasshof?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably just one week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole thing was one week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One long, long week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think everybody, everybody tried to, to follow somebody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, most people really looked up to Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Csato, our friend and cousin, the lawyer.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
